[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0039","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0039.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0007","title":"OpenSSL PKCS#1 填充加密会话信息泄露漏洞","description":"该漏洞由贝尔实验室研究员 Daniel Bleichenbacher 于 1998 年发现，涉及 SSL 协议中 RSA PKCS #1 v1.5 填充方式的侧信道攻击。远程攻击者首先截获客户端与服务器之间的加密 SSL 会话，随后向服务器发送约一百万个精心构造的密文，通过观察服务器返回的填充校验错误差异逐步推断出会话密钥，最终解密被截获的加密通信内容。该漏洞影响 SSLeay 加密库及使用 SSL 协议的大量产品，包括 Microsoft Internet Information Server 3.0/4.0、Netscape Enterprise Server、Exchange Server 5.5 等服务器软件。由于攻击需要大量交互查询，服务器 CPU 和网络流量异常上升可作为检测手段。Microsoft 已于安全公告 MS98-002 中发布修补程序更新 SCHANNEL.dll。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0007"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-06-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:19.650","remediation":"立即将 SSLeay 升级至 OpenSSL 0.9.6 或更新版本，该版本修复了 PKCS #1 填充预言机信息泄露缺陷。如无法升级，在服务端禁用 SSLv2 协议，仅启用 TLS 1.0+，并配置统一的错误返回消息以防止攻击者通过错误响应区分填充格式。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-002"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0039.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1296","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1296.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1038","title":"Tiger 安全审计工具 2.2.3 符号链接攻击任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Tiger 2.2.3 安全审计工具在临时文件处理机制中存在严重漏洞。攻击者可通过操纵默认工作目录（WORKDIR）下的临时文件创建符号链接，诱使程序覆盖原始文件，实现对任意系统文件的写入操作。此漏洞影响虎嗅安全工具的默认配置，攻击者无需网络即可通过本地权限执行攻击，实现文件权限提升和系统文件破坏。攻击过程通过精心构造的符号链接链，实现对目标文件的完全控制，包括读取、修改和删除，可能导致敏感信息泄露或系统崩溃。漏洞利用时攻击者需具备本地用户权限，但一旦成功可获得系统级文件访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1038"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-06-26","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Tiger 安全审计工具至 2.2.4 或更高版本，此版本修复了临时文件创建过程中的符号链接验证漏洞。具体修复措施包括：1. 在创建临时文件时验证文件路径的真实性，防止符号链接攻击；2. 使用原子操作创建临时文件；3. 限制临时文件权限，避免未经授权的访问；4. 建议用户将 WORKDIR 目录权限设置为仅当前用户可访问（chmod 700），并定期清理临时文件以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221103125976&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a3a08d51f200d453300fca8b852aada6b8c5985a/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1038.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1296.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1296.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1296.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1295","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1295.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1037","title":"SATAN 1.1.1 rex.satan 符号链接任意文件覆盖漏洞","description":"SATAN 1.1.1 的 rex.satan 脚本在创建临时文件时使用了固定的绝对路径 /tmp/rex.$$，本地用户可通过预先创建指向目标文件（如系统关键文件或其他用户文件）的符号链接，使 rex.satan 脚本在运行时将内容写入该链接所指向的文件，从而实现任意文件覆盖。攻击者需具备本地访问权限且在目标用户运行 SATAN 之前完成符号链接的布置，可能导致权限提升或破坏系统完整性。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1037"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1998-06-26","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"避免使用固定的 /tmp/rex.$$ 绝对路径创建临时文件，改用 mkstemp 等安全临时文件生成方式，或采用相对路径（如 ./rex.$$）并配合 O_EXCL 标志创建文件；如无法升级，请以受限权限运行 SATAN 并清理 /tmp 下相关临时文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-06-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221103125976&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221103125986&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7167.php","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1037","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a3a08d51f200d453300fca8b852aada6b8c5985a/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1037.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1295.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1294","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1294.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1036","title":"COPS 1.04 符号链接攻击致任意文件覆盖漏洞","description":"COPS 1.04 版本在处理临时文件时存在符号链接攻击漏洞。程序在执行 res_diff、ca.src 和 mail.chk 等组件时，以不安全的方式创建临时文件，未对文件路径进行充分验证。本地攻击者可利用符号链接攻击，在 COPS 创建临时文件前将符号链接指向目标系统文件，从而实现对任意文件的覆盖或创建操作。成功利用此漏洞可导致攻击者获取系统完全控制权限，造成机密性、完整性和可用性的全面丧失。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1036"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1998-06-26","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 COPS 至修复了临时文件符号链接问题的版本，或应用厂商提供的安全补丁。临时缓解措施包括：以受限专用用户身份运行 COPS，将临时目录设置为仅该用户可写（如 chmod 700 /tmp/cops-tmp），并确保程序使用 O_EXCL 标志创建临时文件以防止符号链接攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221103125976&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1294.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1280","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1280.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1479","title":"Matt Wright textcounter.pl 1.2 任意命令执行漏洞","description":"Matt Wright 开发的 textcounter.pl 1.2 是一款用于统计网站访问量的 Perl CGI 脚本。该脚本在处理用户输入时未对特殊字符进行安全过滤，导致远程攻击者可构造包含 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符、反引号等）的恶意请求，将任意系统命令注入到 Perl 脚本执行环境中，从而在目标 Web 服务器上以 CGI 进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响所有运行 textcounter.pl 1.2 版本且将其作为 CGI 程序暴露在网络中的站点，攻击者无需身份认证，仅需向该脚本发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可完成利用，危害程度极高，可造成服务器被完全控制、敏感数据泄露或被用于进一步内网渗透。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1479"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-06-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:31.793","remediation":"建议立即停用并删除 Matt Wright textcounter.pl 1.2 脚本，替换为现代计数器方案（如 JavaScript 客户端计数或服务端数据库计数）。若必须保留 CGI 计数器，请在 Web 服务器层面禁用 CGI 执行权限、配置 mod_security 规则过滤 shell 元字符（; | & $ `），并在防火墙层面限制 CGI 目录仅允许 POST/GET 方法访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/9609","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2265","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2052","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20583","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5b55afba6f3a87fe9319e1de76170e4c2760d614/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1479.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/textcounter_pl.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1280.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1276","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1276.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1442","title":"Linux内核 AMD K6处理器指令序列导致拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux 2.0.x及2.1.x内核中，AMD K6处理器存在一个bug，本地用户通过执行特定的指令序列（可能涉及访问段外地址）可导致系统崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用条件低，本地用户无需特殊权限即可触发，影响系统可用性。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1442"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-06-22","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级Linux内核至2.0.40及以上版本或2.1.133及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续内核版本中修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1442","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/105","http://uwsg.iu.edu/hypermail/linux/kernel/9805.3/0855.html","http://www.cs.helsinki.fi/linux/linux-kernel/Year-1998/1998-25/0816.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1276.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1139","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1139.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0783","title":"FreeBSD 2.2 NFS 设备文件硬链接拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 2.2 及更早版本在通过 NFS 导出文件系统时，未正确限制对设备特殊文件（如 /dev 下的块设备与字符设备）创建硬链接的权限。本地或具有 NFS 挂载访问权限的攻击者可利用此缺陷，在导出的文件系统上创建指向设备文件的硬链接并反复访问，导致系统资源被异常占用或内核处理异常，进而引发拒绝服务。攻击条件为攻击者需能挂载或访问受影响的 NFS 导出目录，并在其中创建硬链接。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0783"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-06-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:02.953","remediation":"建议升级到 FreeBSD 3.0 或更高版本，该问题已在后续版本中修复。若无法立即升级，应限制本地用户对设备特殊文件（/dev 目录）的访问权限，并避免将设备文件所在目录通过 NFS 导出；同时可在挂载 NFS 文件系统时添加 nodev 选项，禁止在该文件系统上解释设备文件，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-057.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/6090","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/19dfa989c2a07b8fd71870a139a7d171f621ff41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0783.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1139.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1324","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1324.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1085","title":"SSH 1.2 CBC/CFB模式加密流数据插入攻击漏洞","description":"SSH 1.2.25、1.2.23 及更早版本在使用 CBC（密码块链接）或 CFB（64位密码反馈）加密模式时存在插入攻击漏洞。远程攻击者利用已知明文攻击，可计算出通过 CRC-32 校验的有效数据包，从而在 SSH 客户端与服务器之间的已加密数据流中插入任意数据。该漏洞影响了早期 SSH 协议的多种实现，威胁数据流完整性与机密性。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1085"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-06-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.383","remediation":"立即升级至 SSH 2.x 协议（如 OpenSSH 3.4p1 及以上版本），在 sshd_config 中配置 Protocol 2 禁用 SSH-1 协议以彻底规避该漏洞。如无法升级，在服务端配置 Ciphers 禁用 CBC 模式密码（如仅使用 aes128-ctr/aes256-ctr），并启用 HMAC 完整性校验（MACs hmac-sha1），同时禁用压缩和转发代理作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221103125884&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221104525878&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/1126.php","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/13877","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1085.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1085","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1085.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1085.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/ssh_insertion.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qfm6-qcw8-g9xg/GHSA-qfm6-qcw8-g9xg.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/phrackzine/articles/blob/02d477c4f24342276683a6150220cf32a7b57929/issues/72/2.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1085.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1324.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1440","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1440.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1271","title":"Macromedia Dreamweaver FTP密码弱加密信息泄露漏洞","description":"Macromedia Dreamweaver 使用弱加密算法存储 FTP 密码，本地攻击者可通过分析加密机制轻易解密其他用户的 FTP 凭据。该漏洞影响多个 Dreamweaver 版本，攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限，利用难度低。由于加密强度不足，存储的密码可被直接逆向还原，导致敏感凭据泄露。建议升级至修复版本或使用更安全的凭据存储方式。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1271"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-06-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:04.950","remediation":"升级至 Macromedia Dreamweaver MX（6.0）及以上版本，这些版本已改用强加密算法保护 FTP 密码存储。如无法升级，建议不在 Dreamweaver 中保存 FTP 密码，每次手动输入；或改用 FileZilla、WinSCP 等支持加密存储密码的专业 FTP 客户端替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/9511","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1636","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1271.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1271","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1271.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1271.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-293r-f52g-2w34/GHSA-293r-f52g-2w34.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87834/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1271.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--6b93ea56-8deb-434d-897e-a18523c0fa79.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1440.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1303","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1303.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1555","title":"Cheyenne InocuLAN Anti-Virus Server 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Cheyenne InocuLAN Anti-Virus Server 4.0 Service Pack 2 之前版本在 Windows NT 4.0 上创建更新目录时错误地设置了 \"EVERYONE FULL CONTROL\" 权限，导致本地用户可向该目录写入恶意 DLL 文件。当杀毒软件执行自动更新功能时，会加载并执行该恶意 DLL，从而实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响运行 InocuLAN 4.0 SP2 前版本的 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者需具备本地登录权限，利用杀毒更新机制植入木马 DLL 实现代码执行与权限提升，CVSS 评分 7.2（高危）。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1555"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-06-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:42.477","remediation":"升级到 Cheyenne InocuLAN 4.0 Service Pack 2 或更高版本以修复更新目录权限配置。若无法立即升级，请以管理员身份手动将 InocuLAN 更新目录的 NTFS 权限从\"Everyone 完全控制\"调整为仅 Administrators 与 InocuLAN 服务账户具备读写权限，并定期核查该目录文件完整性作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/9515","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/106","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1536","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19083","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/68b3c685b96421db99cac9beb9d7bc8a6314be79/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1555.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1555","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1555.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/36499b7630ab4a32d11ab7c901b4c87271211bec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1555.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/645f3b3aab113438413618cef41319453f39d643/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-66v7-mjfq-96pv/GHSA-66v7-mjfq-96pv.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1555.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--716ff60e-b859-41ba-a98f-2b91147668c2.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1303.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1377","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1377.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1178","title":"Sambar Sambar Server 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Sambar Server 4.1 beta 版本中存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求访问 dumpenv.pl 脚本，从而获取服务器环境变量、系统路径等敏感配置信息。该漏洞可被用于进一步的信息收集，辅助后续攻击，影响 Sambar Server 4.1 beta 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1178"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-06-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:53.117","remediation":"立即移除或重命名 Sambar Server 安装目录下 cgi-bin 中的 dumpenv.pl 脚本，以防止远程攻击者通过 HTTP 请求获取服务器环境变量等敏感信息。同时将 Sambar Server 升级至 4.1 以上已修复此问题的最新版本（最高至 6.x），并在 Web 服务器前端通过防火墙或反向代理限制对 cgi-bin 目录的未授权访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/9505","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3223","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1178.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1178","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1178.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1178.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7p9v-gcpq-g972/GHSA-7p9v-gcpq-g972.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/dumpenv.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1178.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000307.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1d9ece17-90a6-4a63-9ab0-8f8a22017a0e.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1377.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1377.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1377.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0145","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0145.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0054","title":"Sun Solaris ftpd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 2.3 至 2.6 版本的 ftpd 守护进程存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统的 FTP 服务发送特制请求，导致 ftpd 进程崩溃或停止响应，造成服务不可用。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，无需特殊权限即可利用，影响范围广泛。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0054"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-06-10","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止支持的 Sun Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1/2.6，官方补丁 Sun Security Bulletin #171 已不可用。建议升级至 Solaris 8 或更高版本以获得修复；如无法升级，可禁用 ftpd 服务（编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 注释 ftp 行后重启 inetd），或使用 tcpwrappers 限制可信来源 IP 访问，并在网络边界防火墙封禁 TCP 21 端口作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0054"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0145.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0040","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0040.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0008","title":"Sun Solaris NIS+ rpc.nisd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 系统中的 NIS+（网络信息服务增强版）rpc.nisd 守护进程存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可导致拒绝服务或在目标系统上以 root 权限执行任意代码。受影响的版本包括 Solaris 2.3、2.4、2.5 和 2.5.1。该漏洞 CVSS v2 评分为 10.0，属于严重级别。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0008"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-06-08","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Sun 官方在 Security Bulletin #170 中发布了针对 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1 的安全补丁。如 NIS+ 服务非业务必需，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释掉 rpc.nisd 条目并重启 inetd 以禁用该服务。同时应在网络边界防火墙阻断对 RPC 端口（111/TCP/UDP）的外部访问。若无法立即打补丁，可结合 TCP Wrappers 配置 hosts.allow/deny 限制可访问 NIS+ 服务的来源 IP。由于相关系统版本已停止支持，建议迁移至替代身份管理方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0008"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0040.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1365","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1365.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1152","title":"Compaq/Microcom 6000 Access Integrator 暴力破解漏洞","description":"Compaq/Microcom 6000 Access Integrator 存在认证机制缺陷，系统未限制失败登录尝试次数，远程攻击者可对用户名和密码实施暴力破解攻击，从而获取未授权访问权限。该漏洞影响 Compaq/Microcom 6000 系列产品，攻击者无需任何身份认证，通过网络即可进行字典式暴力猜解，严重威胁系统安全。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1152"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-06-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:49.910","remediation":"该产品已停止维护，建议升级至支持账户锁定策略的现代访问网关设备。如无法替换，可在网络层面限制源 IP 访问（仅允许受信任管理网段），并部署入侵检测系统监控暴力破解行为作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90296493106214&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1152.json","https://github.com/kenhuangus/llm-wiki/blob/d2bd485921f6c7b6071afbb389f44ab8e4e83c69/wiki/security/cve/cve-1999-1152.md","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1152","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1152.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1152.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-69gg-qrhh-p73q/GHSA-69gg-qrhh-p73q.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_200_300.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88506/info.html","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-307.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1152.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1365.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1364","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1364.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1151","title":"Compaq Microcom 6000 Access Integrator 会话超时未设置导致远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Compaq Microcom 6000 Access Integrator 存在会话超时机制缺失漏洞。该设备在提示输入用户名或密码后未设置会话超时限制，远程攻击者可通过建立连接但不提供任何认证凭据的方式，长期占用会话资源，导致设备无法处理合法用户的认证请求，从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Compaq Microcom 6000 系列设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1151"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-06-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:49.783","remediation":"该产品已停止支持，无官方补丁可用。建议在网络边界防火墙或 ACL 中限制对 Microcom 6000 管理端口的访问，仅允许受信 IP 连接；同时在设备配置中启用连接超时参数（如 idle-timeout），限制未认证连接的持续时间；或迁移至受支持的替代产品彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90296493106214&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2089","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1151.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1151","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1151.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1151.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-93vv-5jr3-4fvj/GHSA-93vv-5jr3-4fvj.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88484/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1151.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--e7ec9f6b-530e-48a8-85d5-73cf1a4e3904.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1364.toml"}]